&quot;It&#39;s your turn,&quot; Clinton&#39;s campaign aide Ian Sams wrote on Twitter in reference to the Democratic presidential nominee&#39;s release.
Michael Cohen, Trump&#39;s special adviser, told CNN on Thursday that he would not allow Trump to release anything until the tax audit is complete.
